comments: Murray (DEN) slightly extends his off-arm against Forbes' (SAS) front at the start of the drive and makes marginal contact.
Forbes (SAS) briefly has his arms around Jokic's (DEN) midsection before correcting.
Forbes (SAS) maintains a legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Murray (DEN) that does not affect his SQBR.
[Observable in enhanced video] RLB shows that Mills (SAS) brings part of his hand underneath the ball and brings it to a pause during his dribble.
RAR shows Harris (DEN) briefly has his arms around Forbes' (SAS) upper half before correcting.
LAR shows Murray (DEN) makes marginal contact with DeRozan's (SAS) right arm at the end of the drive and does not affect his ability to gather.
Jokic (DEN) makes contact with DeRozan's (SAS) arm that affects his dunk attempt before he grabs the rim.  The illegal contact occurs prior to any possible illegal assist in scoring.
Aldridge (SAS) and Jokic (DEN) engage and disengage off-ball without affecting the other's FOM.

LAR shows Aldridge (SAS) makes marginal contact with Harris' (DEN) side as he attempts to get around the pick. Aldridge then makes inadvertent contact to Harris' head/neck area. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Gay (SAS) makes marginal contact with Jokic's (DEN) front/left arm at the end of the drive and does not affect his ability to pass.
RLB shows Jokic (DEN) maintains his pivot foot during the spin move.
Forbes (SAS) makes contact with his forearm to Harris' (DEN) lower half as he is airborne, affecting his shot attempt.

LAR shows Jokic (DEN) makes inadvertent contact with Aldridge's (SAS) head during rebounding. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
LAR shows Millsap (DEN) moves slightly into Mills' (SAS) path prior to contact being made near the free throw line, but it is marginal and does not affect Mills' ability to defend.
Mills (SAS) and Murray (DEN) engage and disengage without affecting the other's FOM.
Aldridge (SAS) briefly has his arm around Jokic's (DEN) midsection before correcting.
Jokic (DEN) firms up in his screening position in Mills' (SAS) path and absorbs the contact as it is made.
RAR shows Murray (DEN) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two legal steps before releasing the pass.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in Mills' (SAS) path and does not deliver the contact.
Craig (DEN) makes marginal body contact with DeRozan (SAS) before cleanly blocking his shot attempt.
LLS shows Jokic (DEN) makes clean contact with the ball before making incidental contact with Aldridge's (SAS) left wrist during rebounding.
Mills (SAS) makes marginal contact with Jokic's (DEN) upper half that does not affect his SQBR.
DeRozan (SAS) is in the lane for longer than three seconds without actively guarding an opponent.
LAR shows Mills (SAS) briefly grasps Jokic's (DEN) jersey, but releases without affecting his FOM.
Jokic (DEN) makes marginal contact with Mills' (SAS) backside during rebounding.
